name: Sander van Doorn
description: '''Sander Ketelaars''' ({{IPA|nl|ˈsɑndər ˈkeːtəlaːrs}}; born 28 February 1979), better known by his stage name '''Sander van Doorn''' ({{IPA|nl|ˈsɑndər vɑn ˈdoːr(ə)n|lang}}) or the initials SvD, is a Dutch [[electro house]] DJ and record producer from [[Eindhoven]].
